<text><body>
<cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">No. 674-9 金剛三昧</cb:mulu><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">金剛別傳</cb:mulu><cb:div type="other">
<lb ed="X" n="0779b15"/><milestone unit="juan" n="11"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0779b16"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0779b17"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">拈金剛經五十三則</cb:mulu>
<lb ed="X" n="0779b18"/><lb ed="R059" n="0309a01"/><cb:div type="xu"><cb:mulu type="序" level="3">金剛小引</cb:mulu><head>金剛小引</head>
<lb ed="X" n="0779b19"/><lb ed="R059" n="0309a02"/><p xml:id="pX37p0779b1901">禾中古資聖寺為鹽官安國師道場。俍亭和尚重來
<lb ed="X" n="0779b20"/><lb ed="R059" n="0309a03"/>繼席。國師嘗云。虗空為鼓。須彌為椎。甚麼人打得。俍
<lb ed="X" n="0779b21"/><lb ed="R059" n="0309a04"/>亭和尚則豈非其人哉。海內嚮慕翹勤非一日矣。夏
<lb ed="X" n="0779b22"/><lb ed="R059" n="0309a05"/>五之月大周直叩座前飽聆禪悅。真炎暑中一帙清
<lb ed="X" n="0779b23"/><lb ed="R059" n="0309a06"/>涼散也。別後挂帆而北。好一柄犀牛扇子直扇清風
<lb ed="X" n="0779b24"/><lb ed="R059" n="0309a07"/>過于虎阜。快甚快甚。至讀所為金剛妙義。則橫說竪
<pb ed="X" xml:id="X37.0674.0779c" n="0779c"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0779c01"/><lb ed="R059" n="0309a08"/>說。權說實說。七縱八橫。翻天倒地。無所不說。究未嘗
<lb ed="X" n="0779c02"/><lb ed="R059" n="0309a09"/>說。空生云。未曾得聞如是之經。大周亦云。未曾得聞
<lb ed="X" n="0779c03"/><lb ed="R059" n="0309a10"/>如是之說也。因合掌恭敬而為之引。</p>
<lb ed="X" n="0779c04"/><lb ed="R059" n="0309a11"/><p xml:id="pX37p0779c0401" rend="margin-left:10em">雲棲弟子大周拜題</p></cb:div>
<lb ed="X" n="0779c05"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0779c06"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">雲溪俍亭挺和尚拈金剛經五十三則</cb:mulu>
<lb ed="X" n="0779c07"/><cb:juan fun="open" n="11"><cb:mulu type="卷" n="11"></cb:mulu><cb:jhead>No. 674-9
<lb ed="X" n="0779c08"/><lb ed="R059" n="0309a13"/> 雲溪俍亭挺和尚拈金剛經五十
<lb ed="X" n="0779c09"/><lb ed="R059" n="0309a13"/>三則</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="X" n="0779c10"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0779c11"/><lb ed="R059" n="0309a14"/><byline cb:type="editor">枯宅居士　楊師益　編</byline>
<lb ed="X" n="0779c12"/><lb ed="R059" n="0309a15"/><entry><form>敷座而坐</form>
<lb ed="X" n="0779c13"/><lb ed="R059" n="0309a16"/><cb:def><p xml:id="pX37p0779c1301" rend="margin-left:1em">拈云。當時忽有人。大展坐具。作禮三拜。拂袖便行。也
<lb ed="X" n="0779c14"/><lb ed="R059" n="0309a17"/>許他具一隻眼。或喝散大眾。掀倒繩床。也許他具
<lb ed="X" n="0779c15"/><lb ed="R059" n="0309a18"/>一隻眼。或將老瞿曇一脚蹋翻。說老老大大。作這
<lb ed="X" n="0779c16"/><lb ed="R059" n="0309b01"/>般行徑。也許他具一隻眼。</p></cb:def></entry>
<lb ed="X" n="0779c17"/><lb ed="R059" n="0309b02"/><entry><form>云何應住云何降伏其心</form>
<lb ed="X" n="0779c18"/><lb ed="R059" n="0309b03"/><cb:def><p xml:id="pX37p0779c1801" rend="margin-left:1em">拈云。空生空生。囈語作麼。好與一頓痛棒。趂出在三
<lb ed="X" n="0779c19"/><lb ed="R059" n="0309b04"/>門外。不許相見。或者有箇入頭。也不見得。善哉善
<lb ed="X" n="0779c20"/><lb ed="R059" n="0309b05"/>哉。教壞人家男女。</p></cb:def></entry>
<lb ed="X" n="0779c21"/><lb ed="R059" n="0309b06"/><entry><form>應如是住如是降伏其心</form>
<lb ed="X" n="0779c22"/><lb ed="R059" n="0309b07"/><cb:def><p xml:id="pX37p0779c2201" rend="margin-left:1em">拈云。空生空生。錯過一機了也。當時若舉起便薦。呵
<lb ed="X" n="0779c23"/><lb ed="R059" n="0309b08"/>呵大笑一場說。原來佛法無多子。豈不通身慶快。
<lb ed="X" n="0779c24"/><lb ed="R059" n="0309b09"/>不唧<g ref="#CB00070">𠺕</g>漢。更疑他三十年。</p></cb:def></entry>
<pb ed="X" xml:id="X37.0674.0780a" n="0780a"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0780a01"/><lb ed="R059" n="0309b10"/><entry><form>我皆令入無餘涅槃而滅度之</form>
<lb ed="X" n="0780a02"/><lb ed="R059" n="0309b11"/><cb:def><p xml:id="pX37p0780a0201" rend="margin-left:1em">拈云。老瞿曇口門尚窄。也只說得一半。狗子便成佛
<lb ed="X" n="0780a03"/><lb ed="R059" n="0309b12"/>也。香臺又作麼生。</p></cb:def></entry>
<lb ed="X" n="0780a04"/><lb ed="R059" n="0309b13"/><entry><form>菩薩但應如所教住</form>
<lb ed="X" n="0780a05"/><lb ed="R059" n="0309b14"/><cb:def><p xml:id="pX37p0780a0501" rend="margin-left:1em">拈云。切忌動著。動著三十棒。</p></cb:def></entry>
<lb ed="X" n="0780a06"/><lb ed="R059" n="0309b15"/><entry><form>若見諸相非相即見如來</form>
<lb ed="X" n="0780a07"/><lb ed="R059" n="0309b16"/><cb:def><p xml:id="pX37p0780a0701" rend="margin-left:1em">拈云。法眼云。諸相非相即不見如來。天童云。一箇說
<lb ed="X" n="0780a08"/><lb ed="R059" n="0309b17"/>如來禪。一箇說祖師禪。會得甚奇特。不會也相許。
<lb ed="X" n="0780a09"/><lb ed="R059" n="0309b18"/>且道會得的也便罷了。不會的却怎生相許。聻。不
<lb ed="X" n="0780a10"/><lb ed="R059" n="0310a01"/>見道。見怪不怪。其怪自敗。</p></cb:def></entry>
<lb ed="X" n="0780a11"/><lb ed="R059" n="0310a02"/><entry><form>法尚應捨何況非法</form>
<lb ed="X" n="0780a12"/><lb ed="R059" n="0310a03"/><cb:def><p xml:id="pX37p0780a1201" rend="margin-left:1em">拈云。火爐裏拈取一莖眉毛得麼。呀呀墮了也。</p></cb:def></entry>
<lb ed="X" n="0780a13"/><lb ed="R059" n="0310a04"/><entry><form>如來得阿耨多羅三藐三菩提耶如來有所說
<lb ed="X" n="0780a14"/><lb ed="R059" n="0310a05"/>法耶</form>
<lb ed="X" n="0780a15"/><lb ed="R059" n="0310a06"/><cb:def><p xml:id="pX37p0780a1501" rend="margin-left:1em">拈云。當時空生只合拍手歸眾。</p></cb:def></entry>
<lb ed="X" n="0780a16"/><lb ed="R059" n="0310a07"/><entry><form>所謂佛法者即非佛法</form>
<lb ed="X" n="0780a17"/><lb ed="R059" n="0310a08"/><cb:def><p xml:id="pX37p0780a1701" rend="margin-left:1em">拈云。綿州附子益州薑。</p></cb:def></entry>
<lb ed="X" n="0780a18"/><lb ed="R059" n="0310a09"/><entry><form>實無有法名阿羅漢</form>
<lb ed="X" n="0780a19"/><lb ed="R059" n="0310a10"/><cb:def><p xml:id="pX37p0780a1901" rend="margin-left:1em">拈云。切忌坐在無事甲裏。</p></cb:def></entry>
<lb ed="X" n="0780a20"/><lb ed="R059" n="0310a11"/><entry><form>於法實無所得</form>
<lb ed="X" n="0780a21"/><lb ed="R059" n="0310a12"/><cb:def><p xml:id="pX37p0780a2101" rend="margin-left:1em">拈云。情知情知。</p></cb:def></entry>
<lb ed="X" n="0780a22"/><lb ed="R059" n="0310a13"/><entry><form>應無所住而生其心</form>
<lb ed="X" n="0780a23"/><lb ed="R059" n="0310a14"/><cb:def><p xml:id="pX37p0780a2301" rend="margin-left:1em">拈云。有者道石女起舞。木人興歌。道得十分。諦當了
<lb ed="X" n="0780a24"/><lb ed="R059" n="0310a15"/>也。住住住。莫將箇現成句子。錯理會他。</p></cb:def></entry>
<pb ed="X" xml:id="X37.0674.0780b" n="0780b"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0780b01"/><lb ed="R059" n="0310a16"/><entry><form>恒河沙</form>
<lb ed="X" n="0780b02"/><lb ed="R059" n="0310a17"/><cb:def><p xml:id="pX37p0780b0201" rend="margin-left:1em">拈云。好世尊撒泥撒沙。迷昧人家眼目。</p></cb:def></entry>
<lb ed="X" n="0780b03"/><lb ed="R059" n="0310a18"/><entry><form>隨說是經</form>
<lb ed="X" n="0780b04"/><lb ed="R059" n="0310b01"/><cb:def><p xml:id="pX37p0780b0401" rend="margin-left:1em">拈云。古人云。咳嗽掉臂無非佛事。莫不是隨說是經
<lb ed="X" n="0780b05"/><lb ed="R059" n="0310b02"/>麼。知解宗徒未免依文解義了也。</p></cb:def></entry>
<lb ed="X" n="0780b06"/><lb ed="R059" n="0310b03"/><entry><form>非般若波羅蜜名般若波羅蜜</form>
<lb ed="X" n="0780b07"/><lb ed="R059" n="0310b04"/><cb:def><p xml:id="pX37p0780b0701" rend="margin-left:1em">拈云。爪籬木杓與我安放一邊。</p></cb:def></entry>
<lb ed="X" n="0780b08"/><lb ed="R059" n="0310b05"/><entry><form>如來無所說</form>
<lb ed="X" n="0780b09"/><lb ed="R059" n="0310b06"/><cb:def><p xml:id="pX37p0780b0901" rend="margin-left:1em">拈云。老瞿曇直得一時口啞。</p></cb:def></entry>
<lb ed="X" n="0780b10"/><lb ed="R059" n="0310b07"/><entry><form>微塵非微塵世界非世界</form>
<lb ed="X" n="0780b11"/><lb ed="R059" n="0310b08"/><cb:def><p xml:id="pX37p0780b1101" rend="margin-left:1em">拈云。且莫向鬼窟裏作活計。</p></cb:def></entry>
<lb ed="X" n="0780b12"/><lb ed="R059" n="0310b09"/><entry><form>三十二相即是非相是名三十二相</form>
<lb ed="X" n="0780b13"/><lb ed="R059" n="0310b10"/><cb:def><p xml:id="pX37p0780b1301" rend="margin-left:1em">拈云。一棒打殺與狗子喫了也。當時如來性命却在
<lb ed="X" n="0780b14"/><lb ed="R059" n="0310b11"/>別人手裏。</p></cb:def></entry>
<lb ed="X" n="0780b15"/><lb ed="R059" n="0310b12"/><entry><form>離一切諸相即名諸佛</form>
<lb ed="X" n="0780b16"/><lb ed="R059" n="0310b13"/><cb:def><p xml:id="pX37p0780b1601" rend="margin-left:1em">拈云。如何是諸佛出身處。東山水上行。老韶陽指東
<lb ed="X" n="0780b17"/><lb ed="R059" n="0310b14"/>話西。扭壞他人鼻孔。</p></cb:def></entry>
<lb ed="X" n="0780b18"/><lb ed="R059" n="0310b15"/><entry><form>此法無實無虗</form>
<lb ed="X" n="0780b19"/><lb ed="R059" n="0310b16"/><cb:def><p xml:id="pX37p0780b1901" rend="margin-left:1em">拈云。八角磨盤空裏走。錯錯錯。話墮了也。</p></cb:def></entry>
<lb ed="X" n="0780b20"/><lb ed="R059" n="0310b17"/><entry><form>在在處處若有此經</form>
<lb ed="X" n="0780b21"/><lb ed="R059" n="0310b18"/><cb:def><p xml:id="pX37p0780b2101" rend="margin-left:1em">拈云。莫眼花好。</p></cb:def></entry>
<lb ed="X" n="0780b22"/><lb ed="R059" n="0311a01"/><entry><form>為人輕賤</form>
<lb ed="X" n="0780b23"/><lb ed="R059" n="0311a02"/><cb:def><p xml:id="pX37p0780b2301" rend="margin-left:1em">拈云。太尊貴生。</p></cb:def></entry>
<lb ed="X" n="0780b24"/><lb ed="R059" n="0311a03"/><entry><form>算數譬喻所不能及</form>
<pb ed="X" xml:id="X37.0674.0780c" n="0780c"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0780c01"/><lb ed="R059" n="0311a04"/><cb:def><p xml:id="pX37p0780c0101" rend="margin-left:1em">拈云。前三三。後三三。畢竟是多少。</p></cb:def></entry>
<lb ed="X" n="0780c02"/><lb ed="R059" n="0311a05"/><entry><form>果報不可思議</form>
<lb ed="X" n="0780c03"/><lb ed="R059" n="0311a06"/><cb:def><p xml:id="pX37p0780c0301" rend="margin-left:1em">拈云。燈籠緣壁上。天台與他寒山竹筒拾得笤<g ref="#CB00416">󰆠</g>。一
<lb ed="X" n="0780c04"/><lb ed="R059" n="0311a07"/>時向摩耶夫人腹中。現身作佛去也。還有人信得
<lb ed="X" n="0780c05"/><lb ed="R059" n="0311a08"/>及麼。若信不及。三十棒自領出去。若信得及。三十
<lb ed="X" n="0780c06"/><lb ed="R059" n="0311a09"/>棒自領出去。</p></cb:def></entry>
<lb ed="X" n="0780c07"/><lb ed="R059" n="0311a10"/><entry><form>云何應住云何降伏其心</form>
<lb ed="X" n="0780c08"/><lb ed="R059" n="0311a11"/><cb:def><p xml:id="pX37p0780c0801" rend="margin-left:1em">拈云。當時好與一喝。待他耳聾三日。別作商量也。不
<lb ed="X" n="0780c09"/><lb ed="R059" n="0311a12"/>致婆婆和和。說箇不了。</p></cb:def></entry>
<lb ed="X" n="0780c10"/><lb ed="R059" n="0311a13"/><entry><form>當生如是心</form>
<lb ed="X" n="0780c11"/><lb ed="R059" n="0311a14"/><cb:def><p xml:id="pX37p0780c1101" rend="margin-left:1em">拈云。五臺山上雲蒸飯。十字街前狗矢天。剎竿頭上
<lb ed="X" n="0780c12"/><lb ed="R059" n="0311a15"/>煎<g ref="#CB05283">䭔</g>子。三箇猢猻夜簸錢。說即儘說。恐太煞了也。</p></cb:def></entry>
<lb ed="X" n="0780c13"/><lb ed="R059" n="0311a16"/><entry><form>滅度無量眾生實無眾生得滅度者</form>
<lb ed="X" n="0780c14"/><lb ed="R059" n="0311a17"/><cb:def><p xml:id="pX37p0780c1401" rend="margin-left:1em">拈云。如何是行鳥道。不逢一人。又說不行鳥道。且道
<lb ed="X" n="0780c15"/><lb ed="R059" n="0311a18"/>行的是。不行的是。</p></cb:def></entry>
<lb ed="X" n="0780c16"/><lb ed="R059" n="0311b01"/><entry><form>實無有法發阿耨多羅三藐三菩提心者</form>
<lb ed="X" n="0780c17"/><lb ed="R059" n="0311b02"/><cb:def><p xml:id="pX37p0780c1701" rend="margin-left:1em">拈云。樹倒藤枯句。歸何處了也。住住住。且與我覓取
<lb ed="X" n="0780c18"/><lb ed="R059" n="0311b03"/>盋盂柄來。</p></cb:def></entry>
<lb ed="X" n="0780c19"/><lb ed="R059" n="0311b04"/><entry><form>實無有法得阿耨多羅三藐三菩提</form>
<lb ed="X" n="0780c20"/><lb ed="R059" n="0311b05"/><cb:def><p xml:id="pX37p0780c2001" rend="margin-left:1em">拈云。落空亡的外道請過一邊。且莫喚鐘作甕。</p></cb:def></entry>
<lb ed="X" n="0780c21"/><lb ed="R059" n="0311b06"/><entry><form>如來者即諸法如義</form>
<lb ed="X" n="0780c22"/><lb ed="R059" n="0311b07"/><cb:def><p xml:id="pX37p0780c2201" rend="margin-left:1em">拈云。喚作如如。早是變了也。王老師通身負墮。口巴
<lb ed="X" n="0780c23"/><lb ed="R059" n="0311b08"/>巴道。向異類中行。</p></cb:def></entry>
<lb ed="X" n="0780c24"/><lb ed="R059" n="0311b09"/><entry><form>一切法皆是佛法</form>
<pb ed="X" xml:id="X37.0674.0781a" n="0781a"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0781a01"/><lb ed="R059" n="0311b10"/><cb:def><p xml:id="pX37p0781a0101" rend="margin-left:1em">拈云。雲門乾矢橛。洞山麻三觔。莫便是這箇道理麼。
<lb ed="X" n="0781a02"/><lb ed="R059" n="0311b11"/>咄。錯會不少。</p></cb:def></entry>
<lb ed="X" n="0781a03"/><lb ed="R059" n="0311b12"/><entry><form>非大身是名大身</form>
<lb ed="X" n="0781a04"/><lb ed="R059" n="0311b13"/><cb:def><p xml:id="pX37p0781a0401" rend="margin-left:1em">拈云。頭長三寸。頸長一尺。畢竟是甚麼人。喚取來。我
<lb ed="X" n="0781a05"/><lb ed="R059" n="0311b14"/>要與他相見。</p></cb:def></entry>
<lb ed="X" n="0781a06"/><lb ed="R059" n="0311b15"/><entry><form>實無有法名為菩薩</form>
<lb ed="X" n="0781a07"/><lb ed="R059" n="0311b16"/><cb:def><p xml:id="pX37p0781a0701" rend="margin-left:1em">拈云。金果朝來猿摘去。玉花晚後鳳<g ref="#CB03340">󰴌</g>歸。道伴交肩。
<lb ed="X" n="0781a08"/><lb ed="R059" n="0311b17"/>這裏莫錯認好。</p></cb:def></entry>
<lb ed="X" n="0781a09"/><lb ed="R059" n="0311b18"/><entry><form>諸心非心是名為心</form>
<lb ed="X" n="0781a10"/><lb ed="R059" n="0312a01"/><cb:def><p xml:id="pX37p0781a1001" rend="margin-left:1em">拈云。有者道剎竿頭上仰蓮心。分明是這箇也。且道
<lb ed="X" n="0781a11"/><lb ed="R059" n="0312a02"/>你面皮厚多少。</p></cb:def></entry>
<lb ed="X" n="0781a12"/><lb ed="R059" n="0312a03"/><entry><form>過去心不可得現在心不可得未來心不可得</form>
<lb ed="X" n="0781a13"/><lb ed="R059" n="0312a04"/><cb:def><p xml:id="pX37p0781a1301" rend="margin-left:1em">拈云。周金剛好不丈夫。被他老婆一問。直得口啞。若
<lb ed="X" n="0781a14"/><lb ed="R059" n="0312a05"/>是箇皮裏有血的。何不與他餅子一擔打翻。</p></cb:def></entry>
<lb ed="X" n="0781a15"/><lb ed="R059" n="0312a06"/><entry><form>福德無故得福德多</form>
<lb ed="X" n="0781a16"/><lb ed="R059" n="0312a07"/><cb:def><p xml:id="pX37p0781a1601" rend="margin-left:1em">拈云。真園頭作許多痴福。著甚來由。好與他念法華
<lb ed="X" n="0781a17"/><lb ed="R059" n="0312a08"/>一齊趂出。免得後人說勝說負。</p></cb:def></entry>
<lb ed="X" n="0781a18"/><lb ed="R059" n="0312a09"/><entry><form>色身非色身諸相非諸相</form>
<lb ed="X" n="0781a19"/><lb ed="R059" n="0312a10"/><cb:def><p xml:id="pX37p0781a1901" rend="margin-left:1em">拈云。金香爐下鐵崑崙。這裏作何分別。</p></cb:def></entry>
<lb ed="X" n="0781a20"/><lb ed="R059" n="0312a11"/><entry><form>若人言如來有所說法即為謗佛</form>
<lb ed="X" n="0781a21"/><lb ed="R059" n="0312a12"/><cb:def><p xml:id="pX37p0781a2101" rend="margin-left:1em">拈云。掩耳盜鈴漢。</p></cb:def></entry>
<lb ed="X" n="0781a22"/><lb ed="R059" n="0312a13"/><entry><form>說法者無法可說</form>
<lb ed="X" n="0781a23"/><lb ed="R059" n="0312a14"/><cb:def><p xml:id="pX37p0781a2301" rend="margin-left:1em">拈云。聾人爭得聞。</p></cb:def></entry>
<lb ed="X" n="0781a24"/><lb ed="R059" n="0312a15"/><entry><form>佛得阿耨多羅為無所得耶</form>
<pb ed="X" xml:id="X37.0674.0781b" n="0781b"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0781b01"/><lb ed="R059" n="0312a16"/><cb:def><p xml:id="pX37p0781b0101" rend="margin-left:1em">拈云。當時翻轉面皮。痛與一頓。儘教扶起沙盆。</p></cb:def></entry>
<lb ed="X" n="0781b02"/><lb ed="R059" n="0312a17"/><entry><form>如是如是乃至無有少法可得</form>
<lb ed="X" n="0781b03"/><lb ed="R059" n="0312a18"/><cb:def><p xml:id="pX37p0781b0301" rend="margin-left:1em">拈云。東瓜直儱侗。</p></cb:def></entry>
<lb ed="X" n="0781b04"/><lb ed="R059" n="0312b01"/><entry><form>是法平等無有高下</form>
<lb ed="X" n="0781b05"/><lb ed="R059" n="0312b02"/><cb:def><p xml:id="pX37p0781b0501" rend="margin-left:1em">拈云。切忌顢頇。</p></cb:def></entry>
<lb ed="X" n="0781b06"/><lb ed="R059" n="0312b03"/><entry><form>修一切善法</form>
<lb ed="X" n="0781b07"/><lb ed="R059" n="0312b04"/><cb:def><p xml:id="pX37p0781b0701" rend="margin-left:1em">拈云。塗污了也。</p></cb:def></entry>
<lb ed="X" n="0781b08"/><lb ed="R059" n="0312b05"/><entry><form>即非善法是名善法</form>
<lb ed="X" n="0781b09"/><lb ed="R059" n="0312b06"/><cb:def><p xml:id="pX37p0781b0901" rend="margin-left:1em">拈云。牛頭出馬頭回。</p></cb:def></entry>
<lb ed="X" n="0781b10"/><lb ed="R059" n="0312b07"/><entry><form>乃至算數譬喻所不能及</form>
<lb ed="X" n="0781b11"/><lb ed="R059" n="0312b08"/><cb:def><p xml:id="pX37p0781b1101" rend="margin-left:1em">拈云。撮空謾語。</p></cb:def></entry>
<lb ed="X" n="0781b12"/><lb ed="R059" n="0312b09"/><entry><form>凡夫非凡夫</form>
<lb ed="X" n="0781b13"/><lb ed="R059" n="0312b10"/><cb:def><p xml:id="pX37p0781b1301" rend="margin-left:1em">拈云。李順王小二烏有先生無是公。一齊向水牯牛
<lb ed="X" n="0781b14"/><lb ed="R059" n="0312b11"/>隊中。打殺了三世諸佛也。惟有謝三郎不在其內。</p></cb:def></entry>
<lb ed="X" n="0781b15"/><lb ed="R059" n="0312b12"/><entry><form>若以色見我以音聲求我是人行邪道不能見
<lb ed="X" n="0781b16"/><lb ed="R059" n="0312b13"/>如來</form>
<lb ed="X" n="0781b17"/><lb ed="R059" n="0312b14"/><cb:def><p xml:id="pX37p0781b1701" rend="margin-left:1em">拈云。切忌當面錯過。</p></cb:def></entry>
<lb ed="X" n="0781b18"/><lb ed="R059" n="0312b15"/><entry><form>於法不說斷滅相</form>
<lb ed="X" n="0781b19"/><lb ed="R059" n="0312b16"/><cb:def><p xml:id="pX37p0781b1901" rend="margin-left:1em">拈云。此事不得孤滯。然雖枯木糝花。要且眼中著屑
<lb ed="X" n="0781b20"/><lb ed="R059" n="0312b17"/>了也。闍黎闍黎放過著。</p></cb:def></entry>
<lb ed="X" n="0781b21"/><lb ed="R059" n="0312b18"/><entry><form>菩薩不受福德</form>
<lb ed="X" n="0781b22"/><lb ed="R059" n="0313a01"/><cb:def><p xml:id="pX37p0781b2201" rend="margin-left:1em">拈云。雖則貧無立錐。只恐富嫌千口。善現善現。且與
<lb ed="X" n="0781b23"/><lb ed="R059" n="0313a02"/>我拈取華房百寶來。</p></cb:def></entry>
<lb ed="X" n="0781b24"/><lb ed="R059" n="0313a03"/><entry><form>無所從來亦無所去</form>
<pb ed="X" xml:id="X37.0674.0781c" n="0781c"/>
<lb ed="X" n="0781c01"/><lb ed="R059" n="0313a04"/><cb:def><p xml:id="pX37p0781c0101" rend="margin-left:1em">拈云。釘釘著懸挂著。</p></cb:def></entry>
<lb ed="X" n="0781c02"/><lb ed="R059" n="0313a05"/><entry><form>一合相非一合相是名一合相</form>
<lb ed="X" n="0781c03"/><lb ed="R059" n="0313a06"/><cb:def><p xml:id="pX37p0781c0301" rend="margin-left:1em">拈云。江南三月鷓鴣啼。算來只在秋江上。且道古人
<lb ed="X" n="0781c04"/><lb ed="R059" n="0313a07"/>語有差別沒差別。聻。</p></cb:def></entry>
<lb ed="X" n="0781c05"/><lb ed="R059" n="0313a08"/><entry><form>如是知如是見如是信解不生法相</form>
<lb ed="X" n="0781c06"/><lb ed="R059" n="0313a09"/><cb:def><p xml:id="pX37p0781c0601" rend="margin-left:1em">拈云。大家吹滅火。一路暗中行。饒你投明到來。也須
<lb ed="X" n="0781c07"/><lb ed="R059" n="0313a10"/>三十拄杖。</p></cb:def></entry>
<lb ed="X" n="0781c08"/><lb ed="R059" n="0313a11"/><entry><form>一切有為法如夢幻泡影如露亦如電應作如
<lb ed="X" n="0781c09"/><lb ed="R059" n="0313a12"/>是觀</form>
<lb ed="X" n="0781c10"/><lb ed="R059" n="0313a13"/><cb:def><p xml:id="pX37p0781c1001" rend="margin-left:1em">拈云。牡丹花且置。即如栢樹子又作麼生。無為法有
<lb ed="X" n="0781c11"/><lb ed="R059" n="0313a14"/>為法變作兩箇熱鐵丸兒。一時穿向金剛鼻孔裏
<lb ed="X" n="0781c12"/><lb ed="R059" n="0313a15"/>去也。具眼人惺惺著。</p></cb:def></entry>
<lb ed="X" n="0781c13"/><lb ed="R059" n="0313a16"/>
